{"id": "art-731", "label": "Art. 731", "title": "Art. 731", "slug": "art-731", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1950157921\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2413\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1950157921\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 73<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_203735148\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2412\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_203735148\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Persoanele care, potrivit art. 6 alin. (2), nu pot fi\nfondatori nu pot fi nici administratori, directori, membri ai consiliului de\nsupraveghere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ai directoratului, cenzori sau\nauditori financiari, iar dac&#259; au fost alese, sunt dec&#259;zute din\ndrepturi.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1391062463\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2411\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1391062463\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin acceptarea mandatului, administratorii, membrii\nconsiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, directorii,\nmembrii directoratului, cenzorii, iar prin încheierea contractului de\nprest&#259;ri servicii, auditorul financiar <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nasum&#259; r&#259;spunderea pentru îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. 6 pentru a <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> exercita aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ie</span>,\nîn contract fiind inclus&#259; o clauz&#259; în acest sens.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}